{
  "title": "MLflow Serving",
  "uid": "mlflow-serving",
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Overview",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 2},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Use **Model** and **Alias** filters to focus on Production vs Test.\nThis dashboard shows health and probe latency for each model@alias."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "MLflow Serve UP (by model@alias)",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 2, "w": 24, "h": 4},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "max by (model, alias) (probe_success{job=\"blackbox-mlflow-serve\", model=~\"$model\", alias=~\"$alias\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{model}}@{{alias}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {"type": "value", "options": {"0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"}, "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}}}
          ],
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}, {"color": "green", "value": 1}]}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "values": false}, "orientation": "horizontal", "textMode": "value", "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "none"}
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "UP instances by alias",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 6, "w": 8, "h": 4},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (alias) (probe_success{job=\"blackbox-mlflow-serve\", model=~\"$model\"})",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "labelsToFields", "options": {}},
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true
            },
            "indexByName": {
              "alias": 0,
              "Value": 1
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "Value": "up_instances"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "options": {"showHeader": true}
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "MLflow Serve latency (probe_duration_seconds)",
      "gridPos": {"x": 8, "y": 6, "w": 16, "h": 8},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "probe_duration_seconds{job=\"blackbox-mlflow-serve\", model=~\"$model\", alias=~\"$alias\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{model}}@{{alias}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "MLflow Serve /ping (details)",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 14, "w": 24, "h": 8},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "probe_success{job=\"blackbox-mlflow-serve\", model=~\"$model\", alias=~\"$alias\"}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {"id": "labelsToFields", "options": {}},
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "indexByName": {
              "Time": 0,
              "model": 1,
              "alias": 2,
              "instance": 3,
              "Value": 4
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "Value": "probe_success"
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "options": {"showHeader": true}
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How to call MLflow Serve",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 22, "w": 24, "h": 5},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Endpoints**\n- Health: `GET /ping`\n- Inference: `POST /invocations`\n\n**Find container**\n- `docker ps --format '{{.Names}}' | grep mlflow-serve-`\n\n**Input schema**\n- MLflow UI → Artifacts → `data_contract/input_schema.json`\n\n**Test alias**\n- Use the dashboard filter **Alias** and select `Test`.\n\n**Note**\nMLflow Serve не публикует метрики количества запросов. Для RPS/ошибок нужен внешний gateway/инструментированный сервис."
      }
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "type": "query",
        "name": "model",
        "label": "Model",
        "datasource": "Prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "sort": 1,
        "query": "label_values(probe_success{job=\"blackbox-mlflow-serve\"}, model)",
        "current": {"text": "All", "value": "$__all"}
      },
      {
        "type": "query",
        "name": "alias",
        "label": "Alias",
        "datasource": "Prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "sort": 1,
        "query": "label_values(probe_success{job=\"blackbox-mlflow-serve\"}, alias)",
        "current": {"text": "All", "value": "$__all"}
      }
    ]
  }
}
